<rss version="2.0" xmlns:content="http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/" xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" xmlns:ss="http://contenthub.aol.com/slideshow/"><channel><title><![CDATA[Engadget is a web magazine with obsessive daily coverage of everything new in gadgets and consumer electronics]]></title><link/> https://www.engadget.com/ <description><![CDATA[Engadget is a web magazine with obsessive daily coverage of everything new in gadgets and consumer electronics]]></description><language>英文</language><copyright>版权所有雅虎 2023</copyright><pubDate> Wed, 21 Jun 2023 21:38:24 +0000</pubDate><generator>雅虎 http://yahoo.com </generator><item><title><![CDATA[Twitter has supposedly started paying its Google Cloud bill again]]></title><description type="html"><![CDATA[<p>据报道，Twitter 已恢复支付其 Google Cloud 合同费用<ins><a data-i13n="cpos:1;pos:1" href="https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-06-21/twitter-resumes-paying-google-cloud-patching-up-relationship?utm_medium=social&amp;cmpid%3D=socialflow-twitter-tech&amp;utm_source=twitter&amp;utm_campaign=socialflow-organic&amp;utm_content=tech&amp;sref=10lNAhZ9#xj4y7vzkg"><em>彭博社</em></a></ins>。如果你错过了即将到来的对决的最初消息， <em>Platformer</em>于 6 月 10 日报道称，在 6 月 30 日续约日期之前，Twitter 一直拒绝向谷歌支付其云服务费用。失去对谷歌基础设施的访问的可能性导致了<ins><a data-i13n="cpos:2;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/twitter-has-reportedly-refused-to-pay-its-google-cloud-contract-161936042.html">疯狂的冲刺</a></ins>Twitter 将尽可能多的服务从谷歌的服务器上迁移出来。然而，据报道，这项工作“落后于计划”，为该公司的一些内部工具在本月底离线打开了大门。</p><p>现在看来 Twitter 已经找到了避免这种情况的方法。<em>彭博社</em>报道<ins><a data-i13n="cpos:3;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/elon-musk-names-nbcu-ad-exec-linda-yaccarino-new-twitter-ceo-155537363.html">琳达·亚卡里诺</a></ins>该公司新任命的首席执行官“帮助我们的关系重回正轨。”事实上，据报道，两家公司正在就更广泛的合作伙伴关系进行谈判，其中可能包括广告和谷歌对 Twitter 付费 API 的使用。 Twitter 没有设立公共关系部门，Engadget 可以联系该部门征求意见。</p><span id="end-legacy-contents"></span><p> Twitter与谷歌云的合同可以追溯到2018年。据<em>彭博社</em>报道，该合同每年使该公司花费2亿至3亿美元，是埃隆·马斯克削减成本的早期目标之一。据报道，谷歌“艰难”地与这位亿万富翁取得联系，讨论 Twitter 未付账单的问题，并一度试图通过 SpaceX 联系他，该公司也与这家科技巨头有业务往来。</p>本文最初发表在 Engadget 上：https://www.engadget.com/twitter-has-supposely-started-paying-its-google-cloud-bill-again-213824844.html?src=rss]]>; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/twitter-has-supposedly-started-paying-its-google-cloud-bill-again-213824844.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> c684b734-3fb7-4233-a0ae-bb9779b5937b</guid><dc:creator>伊戈尔博尼法西奇</dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher>Engadget</dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder> Engadget</dc:rightsholder><pubDate> Wed, 21 Jun 2023 21:38:24 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1687383506</ingested><modified> 2023-06-21T21:38:36+00:00 </modified><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[region|US]]></category><category><![CDATA[language|en-US]]></category><category><![CDATA[author_name|Igor Bonifacic]]></category><media:content height="3667" medium="image" url="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-06/402fb660-1079-11ee-b7ff-8057da3289d3" width="5500"><media:keywords>标题</media:keywords><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[1]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[ ]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[ ]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[ ]]></media:title></media:content><media:content height="3667" medium="image" url="https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-06/402fb660-1079-11ee-b7ff-8057da3289d3" width="5500"><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[2]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[Gonzalo Fuentes / reuters]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[Elon Musk, Chief Executive Officer of SpaceX and Tesla and owner of Twitter, gestures as he attends the Viva Technology conference dedicated to innovation and startups at the Porte de Versailles exhibition c