em>自杀小队</em>游戏</a>版本的 Switch 粉丝兴奋不已。这与其说是为工作室近八年来的第一款新游戏奠定基础，不如说是为了吸引尚未开发的观众。尽管如此，您可能不介意您是该系列的新手还是想重温该系列。如果没有别的，对于那些认为<a data-i13n="cpos:3;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/gotham-knights-october-21-release-date-up-195135689.html"><em>哥谭骑士团</em></a>没有达到<a data-i13n="cpos:4;pos:1" href="https://www.metacritic.com/game/playstation-5/gotham-knights">目标</a>的人来说，它可以作为一种味觉清洁剂。</p>本文最初出现在 Engadget 上，网址为 https://www.engadget.com/batman-arkham-trilogy-comes-to-switch-this-fall-163027577.html?src=rss]]>; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/batman-arkham-trilogy-comes-to-switch-this-fall-163027577.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> 5d44d037-00c5-4f91-96bd-07fa140752f5</guid><dc:creator>乔恩·芬加斯</dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher>Engadget</dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder> Engadget</dc:rightsholder><pubDate> Wed, 21 Jun 2023 16:30:27 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1687363656</ingested><modified> 2023-06-21T16:07:41+00:00 </modified><category><![CDATA[Media]]></category><category><![CDATA[Video Games]]></category><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[region|US]]></category><category><![CDATA[language|en-US]]></category><category><![CDATA[author_name|Jon Fingas]]></category><media:content height="1280" medium="image" url="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-06/2a083f10-1047-11ee-bf7f-d9cc14db649d" width="1920"><media:keywords>标题</media:keywords><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[1]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[ ]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[ ]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[ ]]></media:title></media:content><media:content height="1280" medium="image" url="https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-06/2a083f10-1047-11ee-bf7f-d9cc14db649d" width="1920"><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:id